title: So You Think You Can Dance Australia Season 1 Complete
description: Rogue Traders frontwoman, former Neighbours femme fatale and now host of So You Think You Can Dance Australia Natalie Bassingthwaighte will be joined by a stellar judging panel including international producer and acclaimed choreographer Bonnie Lythgoe, events guru and choreographer Jason Coleman and one of Australia's brightest dancing talents and choreographer Matt Lee.
